metadata.name: Turbo #1
metadata.description: Turbos are NFT collectibles minted on [NPics](https://www.npics.xyz/) for early ecological construction, expressing investors' spiritual aspirations for general NFT development. By issuing Turbos, aka CBBCs(Callable Bull/Bear Contracts), NPics pinoeers a way to strengthen digital awareness among communities, hoping to build a bridge between cultures and values.
